        "text": "谁知道呢？ 或许祂转念心生怜悯， 给你们留下祝福， 使你们可以再次向你们的上帝耶和华献上素祭和奠祭。"
      },
      "cnv": {
        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "有誰知道或許他會轉意，並且施慈愛， 留下餘福， 就是留下獻給耶和華你們的　神的素祭和奠祭。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "或者他轉意後悔，留下餘福， 就是留下獻給耶和華－你們神的素祭和奠祭， 也未可知。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Who knows whether He will not turn and relent And leave a blessing behind Him, Even a grain offering and a drink offering For the Lord your God?"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Who knows? He may turn and relent and leave behind a blessing— grain offerings and drink offerings for the Lord your God."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Who knows? Perhaps he will give you a reprieve, sending you a blessing instead of this curse. Perhaps you will be able to offer grain and wine to the Lord your God as before."
      }
